Description: SDL2-based now playing display for music players
 A simple SDL2-based display for showing currently playing music
 information with support for:
  * Screen rotation (0, 90, 180, 270 degrees)
  * Touch-friendly button controls
  * Album cover art display
  * Material Design icons
  * Multiple display modes (portrait/landscape)
